<!-- ===================== MANIFESTO ===================== -->
<section class="section manifesto">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="manifesto-grid">
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">The idea</span>
        <h2 style="margin-top:18px">Andiswa Imports is <em>not a shop.</em></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="manifesto-body reveal d1">
        <p>There's nothing here to add to a cart. You bring the request  we bring the supply chain.</p>
        <p>Whether it's one item or a full container, we handle the search, the haggling, the quality check and the shipping. <strong>You deal with one person, in Pula (BWP)</strong>, instead of a dozen strangers on the other side of the world.</p>
        <p>You only ever pay once you've seen the price and said yes.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===================== HOW IT WORKS ===================== -->
<section class="section how" id="how">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">How it works</span>
      <h2>From your request to your hands  five steps.</h2>
      <p class="lede">No middle-man maze. One conversation, one price, one delivery. Here's the whole journey.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step reveal">
        <div class="step-num">01</div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h3>Send your request <span class="tag">You</span></h3>
          <p>Describe the product, paste a link, or send a photo. Tell us the quantity and roughly what you'd like to spend. That's all we need to get moving.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step reveal">
        <div class="step-num">02</div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h3>We source &amp; vet <span class="tag">Us</span></h3>
          <p>We hunt down suppliers in China, compare prices, and check the ones worth trusting  ratings, samples, history. The bad ones never reach you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step reveal">
        <div class="step-num">03</div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h3>You get one price <span class="tag">Quote</span></h3>
          <p>A single quote in Pula: product, shipping and our fee, itemised. No hidden mark-ups. Accept it or walk away  no obligation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step reveal">
        <div class="step-num">04</div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h3>We buy &amp; ship <span class="tag">Us</span></h3>
          <p>Once you accept, we pay the supplier, inspect the goods before they leave China, and ship it to your door with a tracking number you can follow.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step reveal">
        <div class="step-num">05</div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h3>You receive <span class="tag">You</span></h3>
          <p>Collect your order at your door. No customs guesswork, no surprise charges. That's it  done.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

