          <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">It depends on the method. Air freight is faster  usually one to two weeks  but costs more per kilo. Sea freight is much cheaper for heavy or bulk orders but takes roughly five to eight weeks. We'll recommend the best option for your order and the exact cost is in your quote.</div></div>
